title: Chamberlain Hill
text: Chamberlain Hill is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> located in the <a href="Catskill%20Mountains">Catskill Mountains</a> of <a href="New%20York%20%28state%29">New York</a> west of <a href="North%20Franklin%2C%20New%20York">North Franklin</a>. <a href="Jackson%20Hill%20%28Delaware%20County%2C%20New%20York%29">Jackson Hill</a> is located east-southeast and <a href="Franklin%20Mountain">Franklin Mountain</a> is located northeast of Chamberlain Hill.
